text.tspan: The openSUSE.Asia Committee is happy to announce

Starting today, the Committee is looking forward to see
your proposals. The committee is looking for speakers
from different avenues representing and advocating Free
Presentations can be submitted in any of the four formats

Papers can be submitted until 3 August 2016.
